    "seo": {
      "title": " CT Lower Abdomen (Including Pelvis) Without Contrast Scan Guide ",
      "description": "Painless, non-contrast CT for lower abdomen/pelvis: Preparation, risks, and same-day results from Cadabams. Know when you need this essential scan.",
